#

Fresh Apple Juice

10 min
$3.5
120 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Beverage

Tags:

BeverageHealthyRefreshing

Description

Refreshing and naturally sweet, this fresh apple juice is the perfect drink to quench your thirst.

Ingredients

  • fresh apples: 4-6
  • water: 1/2 cup
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • sugar (optional): to taste
